
Create user metadata v1.0:
 
 curl -X PUT  -H Content-type:application/json -d @usermd-v1.0.json http://localhost:8080/metadata/user/1.0|tee out.json

Get all entity names:
  curl http://localhost:8080/metadata|tee out.json

Get user versions:
  curl http://localhost:8080/metadata/user|tee out.json

Get user 1.0
  curl http://localhost:8080/metadata/user/1.0|tee out.json

No index in user 1.0, add unique index:

  curl -X PUT -H Content-type:application/json -d@usermd-ei-index.json http://localhost:8080/metadata/user|tee out.json

Get user 1.0
  curl http://localhost:8080/metadata/user/1.0|tee out.json


Create new user schema v2.0, add new field lastLoginDate:

  curl -X PUT -H Content-type:application/json -d@usermd-v2.0.json http://localhost:8080/metadata/user/schema=2.0|tee out.json

Get user versions:
  curl http://localhost:8080/metadata/user|tee out.json

Get user 2.0
  curl http://localhost:8080/metadata/user/2.0|tee out.json


Set v2 as default

  curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/metadata/user/2.0/default|tee out.json





